    <sect1 xml:id="sec-intro">
        <title>Introduction</title>
        <para>This document provides the details for installing Oracle
            WebLogic Server 12cR2 on SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 12 SP2.
            Details are provided for the Intel x86-64 versions of both
            Oracle WebLogic Server 12cR2 and SUSE Linux Enterprise Server
            12. Similar steps apply to other platforms or architectures
            (x86, ia64, IBM Z and LinuxOne, etc.). If you encounter issues
            or have general questions, post your query to
                <email>suse-oracle@listx.novell.com</email>.</para>
        <para>The official Oracle product documentation is available at:
                <link xlink:href="http://docs.oracle.com/en/"/></para>

    </sect1>
