        <sect2 xml:id="sec-install-java">
            <title>Installing Java</title>
            <para>Oracle WebLogic Server 12cR2 (12.2.1.2.0) requires JDK
                version 1.8. Log in to the target system (&sls; 12 SP3
                64-bit operating system) as a non-administration user.
                Download the Java SE Development Kit 8
                (jdk-8u112-linux-x64.tar.gz) from <link
                    xlink:href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/indexes/downloads/index.html#java"
                />. </para>

            <para>Set the environment variables
                    <varname>JAVA_HOME</varname> and
                    <varname>PATH</varname> to ensure the proper JDK
